data.description: Welcome to this stunning MidCentury property nestled in the alcove of Fletcher Hills. This one-of-a-kind home boasts a split-level design and an inviting pool with a backdrop of open mountain views. Step into unparalleled charm as you explore this unique single-family home, featuring panoramic views and modern upgrades, making it a true gem in the neighborhood. The kitchen and bathrooms have been thoughtfully designed with modern amenities and attention to detail. Featuring upgraded flooring throughout, the kitchen boasts restaurant-style appliances, ensuring a culinary experience like no other. The bathrooms exude luxury, with sleek fixtures and elegant finishes, providing a spa-like ambiance for relaxation and re The private backyard oasis offers fruit trees and spacious decks, providing breathtaking mountain vista views. A bonus room, situated off the pool area, is perfect for games and entertainment, enhancing the home's allure. Enjoy the serene ambiance of the private backyard, complete with a sparkling pool and lush fruit trees, while taking in the majestic mountain views from every corner, creating a tranquil retreat right at home.  The largest room, with its own entrance, offers the potential for a lucrative income suite or ADU. Additionally, a bonus area perfect for a yoga studio, gym, or private retreat, provides endless possibilities for customization.
